Mozilla offers no changelog RSS feed(s) I&#x27;m aware of and I don&#x27;t know if there&#x27;s a fitting mailing list. On desktop I update Firefox via my distro&#x27;s package manager and don&#x27;t see any obvious  &quot;what&#x27;s new&quot; notification (a forced new tab opened in the Mozilla builds?), on Android the message appears to only reside under the hamburger menu after updates (not necessarily consistently).<p>Is the only option to generate or create your own RSS feed or email notification setup (preferably separating Windows, OS X and Linux)?<p>---<p>redirecting links for reference:<p>* https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.mozilla.org&#x2F;en-US&#x2F;firefox&#x2F;notes&#x2F;
